Hi James

On 05-Aug-99, James L Boyd wrote:
> Stephen Sweeney churned out *this* drivel:
> 
>> A 030... but this problem only started once I install MagicWB,
>> MagicMenus, ToolsManager, KingCon... actually, it could be MagicMenus or
>> KingCon... Hmmmm..
