>> 
>> Also remove "BB_Debug.prefs" if there is one.
>> 
>> Just delete them all and reboot.  You will have to reset your prefs in
>> SuperTed and the debugger the first time you run Blitz again, but other
>> than that it won't cause any harm.  And it might help.
