@NODE "Mail_153" "Cursor colour"
From: Leigh Parry <lparry@free4all.co.uk>
Date: Wed, 11 Aug 1999 06:18:39 +0000
Subject: Cursor colour
X-UIDL: 71f4c2d69cbc49383190c839b06197ff

Hello,

I'm using Edit$ on my own screen and would like to know if it's possible to
change the colour of the cursor. height of which set with Cursor 4.

I've tried changing the WColour #,# but the cursor remains black. (Colour 0)

Anyone with any help?

Cya,

    Leigh.

