On 31-Aug-99, Leigh Parry wrote:
 
> I've also done sound Function which uses DT's if any body wants that.
> (not currently uploaded) (XBSound & Blitz' Sound libraries caused
> problems, e.g. if using 'SongPlayer', then started a prog with the XB
> or Blitz sound commands 'Songplayer' halted and you couldn't quit out
