Being off topic can be interesting ;-) But how do you know all these facts (or are these expectations) from the AmigaNG? I for one are *very* suspicious about the new computer and especially its proclaimed Amiga-emulator.

Will it be faster than UAE on a PC? Will it really run any software? Will I be able to use Blitz under emulation? And if not, will there be somebody to write a new superbasic variant? (or port the E-compiler ;-) Questions nobody of us can answer at the moment, as we don't know how far Amiga Inc have progressed with their job.

So I'll cross my fingers!

