I am busy using gtshape gadgets in my program. I declare the gtshape so that
it has 2 shapes, one for not pressed and one for pressed. Well if I declare
another one with also 2 shapes, but 2 different ones ofcourse, then the
last(pressed) shape of the second gadget suddenly also becomes the
last(pressed) shape of first gadget.

Ofcourse I have loaded in and declared the shapes the proper way(initshape 
and loadshape). For this I used 4 shapes numbered 1 to 4 and gadget 1 has
shapes 1 and 2 and gadget 2 has shapes 3 and 4.

Any idea what causes this?

Regards

