>> Does anyone know why the Blitz Amiga include files won't include when I
>> try to compile them? 'Duplicate Type', Apparently.

You may have amigalibs.res included as a resident at the same time. It contains
all the stuff from the Blitz OS includes, and you should use it because it
doesn't need to get recompiled everytime, like the separate files.

Or you may have defined a newtype with the same name as another one thats
already in those files.

> This is just a ploy to get that Star-Wars crap in wasn`t it? ;)
> 
