You will (or at least I do) get "Garbage at end of Line" if you save
the includes as ASCII (i.e. if you do the "Edit/Save Block As...) menu
command.    I always highlight the block, Cut it out of the mainline,
flip to the next Blitz window, make sure that is empty with the
Project/New command, paste the block in and then do a Project/Save
from that file.

PS  Anyone got a neater way?

Cheers

-- 
Tony Rolfe
