@NODE "Mail_292" "Re: Indirect Gosub"
From: "Dave" <dave@nbsamiga.demon.co.uk>
Subject: Re: Indirect Gosub
Date: Tue, 10 Aug 1999 02:27:57 +0100
	charset="iso-8859-1"
Encoding: 7bit
X-UIDL: bd51f369f72f2eafb89057f32f0bbd41

Hi Tony,

 You could probably do something like the following

getreg a0,addressofroutine.l
movem.l d0-d7/a0-a6,-(a7)
jsr (a0)                        ;or is it jsr a0 ?? I can never remember
movem.l (a7)+,d0-d7/a0-a6                        ;just to make sure, as the
